## dbt Agents (Enterprise) — How They Complement Exodus

dbt Cloud Enterprise includes native AI agents. Understand the division:

| Capability | dbt Native Agent | Exodus Review Engine |
|-----------|-----------------|---------------------|
| Analyst (NL → SQL, Semantic Layer) | dbt Analyst Agent (beta) | Not in scope |
| Model discovery, catalog browse | dbt Discovery Agent (beta) | Partial via Remote MCP |
| Pipeline observability | dbt Observability Agent (coming) | Exodus anomaly detector |
| Code review, BLOCK/WARN/NOTE | Not available | Exodus PR review (primary) |
| Data diff (CI vs prod) | Not available | Exodus data diff engine |
| Client-specific conventions | Not available | Exodus review-standards YAML |
| Auto-fix BLOCK findings | Not available | Exodus PRHealingAgent |

**Recommended approach:** Enable dbt Analyst Agent for client data consumers. Exodus handles code review and CI. They are additive, not redundant.

